name: Coder
description: Product engineer / tech lead. PR triage, timeboxing, daily standup, and cross-agent product calls across active code projects.

telegram_bot_token_env: CODER_BOT_TOKEN

# Triage + planning is mostly reasoning. Sonnet is the sweet spot.
# Bump per-message with /model opus for hairy reviews or architecture calls.
model: claude-sonnet-4-6
